name: DocType
description: DocType is a Table / Form in the application.

fields.name: u13kl8l6v6
fields.label: Protect Attached Files
fields.description: Users are only able to delete attached files if the document is either in draft or if the document is canceled and they are also able to delete the document.

fields.name: u13infq6pk
fields.label: Naming Rule
fields.options:
Set by user
Autoincrement
By fieldname
By "Naming Series" field
Expression
Expression (old style)
Random
UUID
By script

fields.name: u13abivrnb
fields.label: Is Submittable
fields.description: Once submitted, submittable documents cannot be changed. They can only be Cancelled and Amended.

fields.name: u13fe0oa6e
fields.label: Is Child Table
fields.description: Child Tables are shown as a Grid in other DocTypes

fields.name: u13ji111uv
fields.label: Is Single
fields.description: Single Types have only one record no tables associated. Values are stored in tabSingles

fields.name: u13v7a02cn
fields.label: Is Tree
fields.description: Tree structures are implemented using Nested Set

fields.name: u13nma5tlg
fields.label: Quick Entry
fields.description: Open a dialog with mandatory fields to create a new record quickly. There must be at least one mandatory field to show in dialog.

fields.name: u132hng382
fields.label: Track Changes
fields.description: If enabled, changes to the document are tracked and shown in timeline

fields.name: u13bvsma4i
fields.label: Track Seen
fields.description: If enabled, the document is marked as seen, the first time a user opens it

fields.name: u13klt12oh
fields.label: Track Views
fields.description: If enabled, document views are tracked, this can happen multiple times

fields.name: u13qnkpors
fields.label: Queue in Background (BETA)
fields.description: Enabling this will submit documents in background

fields.name: u13sal336t
fields.label: Timeline Field
fields.description: Comments and Communications will be associated with this linked document
